partnerDetails.about:
At Kinetic Electrical we listen to our clients
We make sure we understand fully what’s required, we prepare for the job at hand and we deliver the “right” solution. We have the systems and work practices that ensure our clients receive a service which is both efficient and professional, with minimal disruption to their business, workplace or home. We deliver this at a price that represents the best possible value for money.

Providing electrical services to the Kapiti Coast area including; Levin, Otaki, Waikanae, Paraparaumu, Whitby, Porirua
